{"lemma":"خُطَّةُ","slug":"خُطَّةُ","root":"خ.ط.ط","root_slug":"خ-ط-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ط-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10942","n10943"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"project, projected course, plan","examples":[{"text":"لَا أَسْتَطِيعُ أَنْ أُصَدِّقَ أَنَّهُ أَفْشَى الخُطَّةَ السِّرِّيَّةَ لِلصَّفِّ بِأَكْمَلِهِ.","english":"I can't believe he blabbed out the secret plan to the whole class."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plot, land, territory, region"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xutˤ.tˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10942","headword_ar":"خُطَّةٌ","root":"xT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~N","text_ar":"خَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An affair: a matter: a case: an event: a state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTobN","text_ar":"خَطْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAlN","text_ar":"حَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAlapN","text_ar":"حَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dubious affair, of great magnitude"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moment, to accomplish which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to perform which, one finds not the way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 436:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumotuhu xuT~apa xasofK","text_ar":"سُمْتُهُ خُطَّةَ خَسْفٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I required,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constrained, him to do an affair of difficulty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to become in a state of abasement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~apa suwo'K","text_ar":"خُطَّةَ سُوْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an evil affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwayukal~ifuniY xuT~apF mina Alxasofi","text_ar":"هُوَيُكَلِّفُنِى خُطَّةً مِنَ الخَسْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He requires,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constrains, me to do an affair of difficulty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (JK. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasofN","text_ar":"خَسْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And it is said in a trad., of Keyleh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayulaAmu A@bonu h`*ihi A^ano yafoSila","text_ar":"اَيُلَامُ ا@بْنُ هٰذِهِ اَنْ يَفْصِلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxuT~apa wayanotaSira mino waraA='i AlHajazapi","text_ar":"الخُطَّةَ وَيَنْتَصِرَ مِنْ وَرَا=ءِ الحَجَزَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Is the son of this"},{"kind":"text","text":"woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be blamed for deciding the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"matter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and defending himself in the absence of the wrongdoers who would prevent his obtaining his right;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those who defend men, one from another, and decide between them justly?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: i. e., when a dubious event, to the encountering of which he does not find the right way, befalls him, that he should not care for it, but decide it so as to settle it and extricate himself from it. (S, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjizN","text_ar":"حَاجِزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Also, in a trad. respecting El-Hodeybiyeh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAyasoA^luwniY xuT~apF","text_ar":"لَايَسْالُونِى خُطَّةً"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuEaZ~imuwna fiyhaA HurumaAti A@ll~`hi taEaAlaY A_il~aA A^aEoTiyotuhumo A_iy~aAhaA","text_ar":"يُعَظِّمُونَ فِيهَا حُرُمَاتِ ا@للّٰهِ تَعَالَى اـِلَّا اَعْطِيْتُهُمْ اـِيَّاهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They shall not ask of me a matter wherein they honour the sacred things of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exalted be He,"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but I will grant it to them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And in the same,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qado EaraDa Ealayokumo xuT~apa ru$odK faA@qobaluwhaA","text_ar":"قَدْ عَرَضَ عَلَيْكُمْ خُطَّةَ رُشْدٍ فَا@قْبَلُوهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hath proposed to you a case of evident rectitude; therefore do ye accept it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And Taäbbatasharrà says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"humaA xaT~ataA A_im~aA A_isaArN wamin~apN\n                      \n                     \n                        waA_im~aA damN waAlqatolu biAlHur~i A^ajodaru"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are two case; either bondage and reproach, or else blood; and slaughter is more befitting to the free,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ingenuous"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: he means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~ataAni","text_ar":"خُطَّتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S. [See Ham p. 34.]) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A course:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~apN naAy^iyapN","text_ar":"خُطَّةٌ نَايِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A distant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far-extending, course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu*o xuT~apF","text_ar":"خُذْ خُطَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu*o xuT~apa AlAinotiSaAfi","text_ar":"خُذْ خُطَّةَ الاِنْتِصَافِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Take thou the course of exacting thy right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, with equity"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotaSifo","text_ar":"اِنْتَصِفْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exact thou thy right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, with equity"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A proof; an evidence; a testimony; an argument; a plea;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an allegation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huj~apN","text_ar":"حُجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TA.) So in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqimo EalaY h`*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"اَقِمْ عَلَى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixuT~apK","text_ar":"بِخُطَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Establish thou a proof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against this thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as is said in the “ Nawádir. ” (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An object of want which one has determined to accomplish:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wafiY raA^osihi xuT~apN","text_ar":"وَفِى رَاْسِهِ خُطَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came having in his mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his head"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of want"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. : [but see the last sentence in this paragraph:] the vulgar say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobapN","text_ar":"خُطْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, L:) the former is the word used by the Arabs: (L:) the latter, however, occurs in the “ Nawádir ” of AZ; therefore the attribution of it to the vulgar demands consideration. (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Boldness to undertake affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ignorance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY raA^osihi xuT~apN","text_ar":"فِى رَاْسِهِ خُطَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his head is ignorance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it has another meaning explained above. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","JK","TA","Msb","L"]},{"entry_id":"n10943","headword_ar":"خِطَّةٌ","root":"xT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land, which a man takes to himself, and upon which he makes a mark, in order to its being known that he has chosen it to build there a house;"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaT","text_ar":"خِطَط"},{"kind":"text","text":"of El-Koofeh and of El-Basrah: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a house, which a man takes to himself, and upon which he makes a mark, in land not possessed, that he may have it for himself exclusively, and build there;"},{"kind":"text","text":"this being done when the Sultán gives permission to a number of the Muslims to found houses in a particular place, and to make their abodes there, as they did in El-Koofeh and El-Basrah: (L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place which is taken and marked for building houses,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for habitation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) or, as is said in the Bári',"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land, which a man takes to himself, and upon which he makes a mark, it not having belonged to any one before him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiT~N","text_ar":"خِطٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) which latter is explained by IDrd as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place which one takes to himself, and marks, from other places:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB, L:) or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of land in which one alights and takes up his abode, none having done so before him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the pl. of the former is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiTazN","text_ar":"حِطَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN bay~inN xiTaTi AlmakaArimi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ بَيِّنٌ خِطَطِ المَكَارِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one exhibits in himself the marks of generous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honourable, qualities"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","Mgh","Msb","IB","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}